@startuml CMU-RERC-APT_tiramisu3-pr

[Mobile Client] as Client
[Java Frontend] as Frontend
[Backend Data Processing] as Backend
[Python Predictor] as Predictor
queue "AWS SQS" as MessageQueue
database "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB
database "Postgres DB" as PostgresDB

Client --> Frontend : HTTP Requests
Frontend --> Client : HTTP Responses

Frontend --> Backend : Fetch Real-time Data
Frontend --> Predictor : Request Predictions
Frontend --> PostgresDB : Log User Interactions

Backend --> MessageQueue : Publish Transit Updates
Backend --> DynamoDB : Store Transit Data

Predictor --> PostgresDB : Fetch Historical Data
Predictor --> Frontend : Provide Predictions

MessageQueue --> Backend : Consume Transit Updates

note right of Backend
  FeedGrabber
  ObservationProcessor
  DynamoCleaner
end note

note right of Frontend
  SchedulesForLocationServlet
  WriteFavRouteServlet
  ReadFavRouteServlet
  StatusLogServlet
  ButtonLogServlet
  FocusLogServlet
  AlarmProcessor
end note

note right of Client
  FavRoutesService
  FavStopsService
  AlarmService
  HandleSettingsService
end note

@enduml